==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-al]]'' (correlative suffix of reason)

===Correlative===
'''ial'''

# for [[some]] reason (indeterminate correlative of reason)
#: As with other indeterminate correlatives in Esperanto, ''[[ial]]'' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality.  '''''Ial''' ajn'' thus means ''for any reason'' or ''why ever''.

